00438 void ParameterNameValueTypeTest::ConvertWStringToMIMEText(MIMEValue& value, const std::wstring& s)
00439 {
00440         u_int32_t len = (u_int32_t) s.length();
00441         u_int16_t* buf = new u_int16_t[len];
00442         for (u_int32_t i=0; i<len; ++i)
00443         {
00444                 buf[i] = (u_int16_t) s[i];
00445                 buf[i] = htons(buf[i]);
00446         }
00447         value.SetValue(buf, len*sizeof(u_int16_t));
00448         delete[] buf;
00449 }
00450 
00451 void ParameterNameValueTypeTest::ConvertStringToMIMEText(MIMEValue& value, const std::string& s)
00452 {
00453         u_int32_t len = (u_int32_t) s.length();
00454         value.SetValue(s.c_str(), len);
00455 }

00457 void ParameterNameValueTypeTest::FillMIMEValue(u_int32_t value, MIMEValue& mime)
00458 {
00459         char buf[NUMBER_BUFFER_LEN];
00460         memset(buf, 0, NUMBER_BUFFER_LEN);      // for aesthetics
00461         value = htonl(value);
00462         memcpy(buf, &value, sizeof(u_int32_t));
00463         mime.SetValue(buf, NUMBER_BUFFER_LEN);
00464 }
